```plantuml
@startuml nikmis_xentrace-analysis
actor User

participant "Xentrace-analysis.c" as Main
participant "xentrace" as Xentrace
participant "Reader.c" as Reader
participant "EventHandler.c" as EventHandler
participant "Event.c" as Event
participant "Analysis Tool" as Analysis

User -> Main: Start analysis
Main -> Xentrace: Spawn xentrace process
Xentrace -> Main: Trace data output
Main -> Reader: Parse trace data
Reader -> Event: Create Events
Event -> Reader: Return Events

loop Event Processing
    Reader -> EventHandler: Dispatch Event
    EventHandler -> Analysis: Invoke Handler
    Analysis -> EventHandler: Return results
end

Main -> User: Display Analysis Results
Main -> Xentrace: Terminate process
@enduml
```